# Commit & Push Workflow

When the user asks to "commit and push" or "create a milestone summary and push":

## 1. Update Notification Bell

Before committing, update the `MOCK_NOTIFICATIONS` array in `src/components/Notifications/NotificationBell.tsx`:

- Add new milestone notifications at the **top** of the array
- Use sequential IDs like `milestone-1`, `milestone-2`, etc.
