## 2. Commit Message Format

Use conventional commit format:
```
feat: Brief summary of changes

- Bullet point details
- Another detail
```

## 3. Push to Remote

Always push to `origin main` after committing.

## 4. Also Update milestoneNotifications.ts (Optional)

For major milestones, also update `src/utils/milestoneNotifications.ts` with the `SESSION_MILESTONES` array for programmatic access to milestone data.
